Vitalk is an AI-powered digital assistant for mental health that helps HR departments transform their company cultures to encourage mental wellness. The company accomplishes this by offering (1) digital tools: a full range of digital conversations and therapeutic interventions to share with employees, (2) progress tracking: insights on a populational level including potential causes of mental health issues, benchmarking, suggestions of interventions, and evolution over time and (3) virtual therapy: text-based coaching or video sessions.

Vixtra is a foreign trade fintech that works as a payment method between importers and exporters, allowing international suppliers to offer extended payment terms and importers to pay their purchases over time. The platform allows importers to release working capital, get confidence and data related to its suppliers, in addition to providing other financial services and visibility of the import processes.
